54
00:02:49,386 --> 00:02:53,785
Suamiku hanyalah orang kaya baru!

55
00:02:53,786 --> 00:02:55,485
Ketika putraku harus mengikuti ujian,

56
00:02:55,486 --> 00:02:57,885
